            release form to participate in an introductory or discovery flight.
            This form is included in new student and rental applications already
            and does not need to be completed separately.
          </dd>
          <div class="mt-9 flex justify-center">
            <a
              href="https://forms.zohopublic.com/SummitFlight/form/LiabilityAgreement/formperma/ACm-MKrCxagTAszh8Qft0FWppBVJD_dv1XxSdZuHoaM"
