            CFI + Instrument certificate. If you are a CFII and wish to be
            considered for future instructing opportunities, please visit our
            Teach at Summit page, review the qualifications we look for, and
            submit your interest from that page.
          </dd>
          <div class="mt-9 flex justify-center">
            <a href="/career/teach-at-summit" class="absolute bottom-12 btn-red"
              >Teach at Summit</a
